nodes.text: Doctor Aphra 14 is the upcoming fourteenth  issue of the canon comic series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra, and is part of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters event. The comic will be written by Alyssa Wong, illustrated by Minkyu Jung, and published by Marvel Comics on September 1, 2021.
